Enum SvgPathCmd

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<SvgPathCmd>
camzup.core.SvgPathCmd
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<SvgPathCmd>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum SvgPathCmd
extends java.lang.Enum<SvgPathCmd>
Command that describes how to render a shape in the d attribute of a path node in scalable vector graphics (SVG).
